import { Image } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default function FeatureIcon({ src, alt, Link }) {
  return (
    <Link to={Link}>
      <Image src={src} alt={alt} borderRadius="full" boxSize="150px" />
    </Link>
  );
}
